{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 08:47:31.227529", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission summary:\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): host_2_1_1_1\n- Root cause: host_incorrect_netmask\n\nRationale:\nhost_2_1_1_1 is configured with 10.2.1.2/8 instead of /24. The /8 mask causes the host to treat 10.200.0.0/24 as on-link, ARP directly, and never send traffic to its default gateway, resulting in Destination Host Unreachable for DNS and web servers. Control-plane (OSPF) and other services (DNS, HTTP listener) are healthy.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2322, "output_tokens": 135, "total_tokens": 2457, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2176}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
